        "authorId" : "3285299a-bae4-44bb-b894-6dd519d37c9e",
        "body" : "I found this, which we can use:\r\n```\r\n--max-doc-length=n   set maximum allowed doc line length and perform these\r\n                       checks (unchecked if not set)\r\n```\r\nRef: https://pycodestyle.pycqa.org/en/latest/intro.html#example-usage-and-output\r\n\r\nBut yeah, good point on how SciPy ignores this (?)",
